## FEATURE 6 — Patient Linking (Animal Context on Checkout)

### Goal

Link checked-out equipment to a specific patient (`vt_animals`) for clinical tracking and billing.

### Schema (server/db.ts)

Confirm `vt_animals` exists (if not, create minimal version):

```typescript
export const vtAnimals = pgTable('vt_animals', {
  id: serial('id').primaryKey(),
  clinicId: text('clinic_id').notNull(),
  name: text('name').notNull(),
  species: text('species'),
  ownerId: text('owner_id'),
  admittedAt: timestamp('admitted_at').defaultNow(),
  dischargedAt: timestamp('discharged_at'),
});
```

Add to the `checkouts` table (or equivalent):

```typescript
patientId: integer('patient_id').references(() => vtAnimals.id),
patientNotes: text('patient_notes'),
```

Define Drizzle relation:

```typescript
export const checkoutsRelations = relations(checkouts, ({ one }) => ({
  patient: one(vtAnimals, {
    fields: [checkouts.patientId],
    references: [vtAnimals.id],
  }),
}));
```

### API

- `GET /api/animals/active` — returns animals currently admitted (`dischargedAt IS NULL`) for the clinic. Used for the patient search.
- `POST /api/checkouts` — extend to accept `patientId?: number` and `patientNotes?: string`
- `GET /api/checkouts/:id` — extend response to include `patient` (joined)

### Frontend

In the checkout form/modal:

- Add a Shadcn `Combobox` (searchable dropdown) labeled `"שייך למטופל (אופציונלי)"`
- Populated from `GET /api/animals/active`
- Shows: `[name] — [species]` per option
- If patient selected, show an optional `Textarea` for `patientNotes`
- In equipment detail view, show active patient link if `checkout.patientId` exists:
  - `PawPrint` icon (Lucide) + patient name + `"מאושפז כרגע"`
  - Subtle `bg-blue-50 border-blue-200` card section
- Add types to `src/types/checkout.ts`:
  
  ```typescript
  patientId?: number | null;
  patientNotes?: string | null;
  patient?: { id: number; name: string; species?: string };
  ```

### Tests (Feature 6)

Create `server/tests/patientLinking.test.ts`:

```typescript
// ✅ POST /api/checkouts saves patientId when provided
// ✅ POST /api/checkouts succeeds with patientId omitted (optional field)
// ✅ POST /api/checkouts rejects patientId that belongs to a different clinic
// ✅ GET /api/checkouts/:id returns nested patient object when patientId is set
// ✅ GET /api/checkouts/:id returns patient: null when patientId is null
// ✅ GET /api/animals/active returns only animals where dischargedAt IS NULL
// ✅ GET /api/animals/active is scoped to clinicId
```

Create `src/tests/PatientCombobox.test.tsx`:

```typescript
// ✅ Combobox renders with placeholder when no patient is selected
// ✅ Combobox options display '[name] — [species]' format
// ✅ Selecting a patient shows the patientNotes textarea
// ✅ patientNotes textarea is hidden when no patient is selected
// ✅ Patient badge renders in equipment detail view when patientId is set
// ✅ Patient badge does not render when patientId is null
```

